---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-auto bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200 py-8">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-indigo-600 text-white p-1 rounded-md">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="16" height="20" x="4" y="2" rx="2"/><line x1="8" x2="16" y1="6" y2="6"/><line x1="16" x2="16.01" y1="10" y2="10"/><line x1="12" x2="12.01" y1="10" y2="10"/><line x1="8" x2="8.01" y1="10" y2="10"/><line x1="16" x2="16.01" y1="14" y2="14"/><line x1="12" x2="12.01" y1="14" y2="14"/><line x1="8" x2="8.01" y1="14" y2="14"/><line x1="16" x2="16.01" y1="18" y2="18"/><line x1="12" x2="12.01" y1="18" y2="18"/><line x1="8" x2="8.01" y1="18" y2="18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">SmartCalc<span class="text-indigo-600">Hub</span></span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4 max-w-sm">
          提供實用、精準且介面美觀的線上計算工具，幫助您更好地規劃個人財務與生活。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">理財工具</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
          <li><a href="/calculators/compound-interest" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">複利計算器</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calculators/mortgage" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">房貸試算</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calculators/roi" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">投資報酬率 (ROI)</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">實用工具</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
          <li><a href="/calculators/salary" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">薪資稅務試算</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calculators/discount" class="hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">折扣計算機</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 text-center text-sm text-slate-400">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} SmartCalc Hub. All rights reserved. 僅供參考，不構成投資建議。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
